{"type": "article", "id": 26863, "title": "可以自由调整的木质台灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-16T06:45:38Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 43, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115758lu37a4hDEFKYmNQ8.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>用“两根木头互相吸引变成了一盏台灯”来形容来自 PT Life 的颠覆性设计其实并不算夸张。这款 Gravity Light 走的是极简的路线，重量仅为 0.8 千克，上下两端都使用磁铁进行连接，不仅便于携带而且组装也很容易。除此之外，LED 灯的部分还能够 360 度旋转，可以根据需要自由调整。如果你对它感兴趣的话可以通过<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/gravity-light-a-360-degree-magnetic-led-lamp--2#/\">链接</a>参与众筹，售价为 69 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115753wBRu7mFh1aQK4zLM.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.73235294\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115753OuiYzalfIVs95BLE.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115755n9AHQfOgo4eGbxFd.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115756GgJzb95fHoa6DXCs.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}